summary:
- **Substantial Holder Update**: Resolution Capital Limited has acquired a 5.04% stake in National Storage REIT (70,169,444 ordinary shares) as of 12/06/2025.  
- **Nature of Interest**: Resolution Capital controls voting/disposal rights via its role as investment manager.  
- **Acquisition Details**: Majority of shares were purchased in open market transactions between February–June 2025 (detailed in Annexure C).  

No other material capital markets or trading impacts identified.
